arts.ttl: Monaco teenagers star in win at Strasbourg
arts.sum: Eliesse Ben Seghir scored twice and fellow teenager George Ilenikhena added the other goal as Monaco rallied to win at Strasbourg 3-1 in the French league on Saturday. The win moved second-placed Monaco three points behind leader Paris Saint-Germain, which played at Angers later Saturday.
